review: I have been a patient of Dr Sachin for the past 12 years. I‚Äôve always loved his work, he is a perfectionist! He is friendly, compassionate and very professional. Going to the dentist is not my favorite thing to do but I know I‚Äôm in good hands with Dr Sachin and his staff. I specially travelled from Gujarat to Mumbai for wisdom tooth extraction and a root canal. He made sure that both teeth on my left lower jaw next to each other were treated in a way that within just 6 days of my stay the surgery happened and stiches healed just in time to fix the root canal cap! Its not that there are no good dentists in Gujarat but I trust him specially not only for the painless treatment but am sure that once he cures a tooth that's FOREVER, it will not required any treatment again.
